pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, January 20, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Wednesday, January 20, 2016:

Davos-Klosters

The Prime Minister will be in private meetings at the World Economic Forum (WEF) throughout the day.

Davos-Klosters

9:20 a.m. EST/3:20 p.m. CET The Prime Minister will deliver an address at the WEF Signature Session.

PMO Media Relations: 613-957-5555
